race.description: Lesley Ann Leonard Memorial Final F
race.comment: BLAZING TURBO (8) was a last start winner (22.66) at this track who is building a strong winning record. Hard to knock his form from this box, unbeaten in two starts. Looks the one to beat. MASTER MCGRAW (1) eye-catching debut run after settling well back but winding up strongly into the frame when second (23.00) at this track over 400m. Has the inside draw this time. Can improve further this time. LITTLE KING (2) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by 2 lengths at this track in a handy 22.96 beating PONTELLA. In great recent form and expected to measure up again. ADA TARO (7) is last start winner who looks one of the chances.
